      • setCustomInstrumentation

        boolean setCustomInstrumentation(WorkQueueInstrumentation instrumentation)
        Saves custom instrumentation. Returns false if could not convert the instrumentation to JSON (e.g. it was too big). Conversion errors are expected are logged.
        Parameters:
        instrumentation - custom instrumentation to save.

      • getOrCreateCustomInstrumentation

        WorkQueueInstrumentation getOrCreateCustomInstrumentation(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,WorkQueueInstrumentationFieldType> fieldTypes)
        Gets custom instrumentation. Parsing errors are expected and logged, an empty object (not null) is returned in case of a parsing error error.
        Parameters:
        fieldTypes - instrumentation fields. This is required because instrumentation fields definition might be changed after instrumentation was saved previous time.
        Returns:
        WorkQueueInstrumentationFieldType, never null.

      • getCustomInstrumentation

        WorkQueueInstrumentation getCustomInstrumentation(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,WorkQueueInstrumentationFieldType> fieldTypes)
        Gets custom instrumentation.
        Parameters:
        fieldTypes - instrumentation fields. This is required because instrumentation fields definition might be changed after instrumentation was saved previous time.
        Returns:
        WorkQueueInstrumentationFieldType, never null.
        Throws:
        org.json.JSONException - if JSON string saved in the database cannot be parsed.
